PROPERTY_LOCATION.NAME: Base Address
PROPERTY_LOCATION.DESCRIPTION: This base address is the base address used by SW to program SMSET

PROPERTY_STRING.NAME: Signal Type
PROPERTY_STRING.DESCRIPTION: The option of setting signal type for event detection

PROPERTY_STRING.NAME: Msg Generation Type
PROPERTY_STRING.DESCRIPTION: The option of event detection in sampling window or permanently detected

PROPERTY_INTEGER.NAME: Sampling Window(cycles)
PROPERTY_INTEGER.DESCRIPTION: The sampling window size expressed as clock cycles(0-0xFF)

PROPERTY_BOOL.NAME: Start on Ext. Trigger
PROPERTY_BOOL.DESCRIPTION: Start Detection on an external trigger

PROPERTY_BOOL.NAME: Stop on Ext. Trigger
PROPERTY_BOOL.DESCRIPTION: Stop Detection on an external trigger

PROPERTY_STRING.NAME: Trace Control
PROPERTY_STRING.DESCRIPTION: Options to control the generation of trace stream

PROPERTY_BOOL.NAME: Timestamp Enable
PROPERTY_BOOL.DESCRIPTION: Enable or disable timestamp in trace data

PROPERTY_INTEGER.NAME: Sync Count(bytes)
PROPERTY_INTEGER.DESCRIPTION: Counts the number of bytes between Synchronization packets(0-0xFFF)

PROPERTY_STRING.NAME: Event Selection
PROPERTY_STRING.DESCRIPTION: Option of enabling or disable individual events
